<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Password Change Request</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h1, p {
            margin: 10px 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        a {
            color: #007bff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #fff;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Password Change Request</h1>
        <p>Hello,</p>
        <p>You've requested to change your password. To proceed with the change, please click on the following link:</p>
        <p><a class="button" href="http://domain.com/passwordChange?token={{token}}">Change Password</a></p>
        <p>If you didn't request this change, you can ignore this email.</p>
        <p>Thank you!</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>